<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="27" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="27">Distribution, habitat, and remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="27">This species inhabits wet lowland forest. It is recorded from French Guiana, eastern Ecuador, Peru, Bolivia, and Brazil (PA, MT).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
